[DQR.IFRS.0105.9556] The following elements are in the presentation linkbase of 04 - Rahavirtalaskelma but are not included in any calculation relationship in the filing. ifrs-full:PaymentsOfLeaseLiabilitiesClassifiedAsFinancingActivities, ifrs-full:ProceedsFromExerciseOfOptions, ifrs-full:PaymentsToAcquireOrRedeemEntitysShares, ifrs-full:RepaymentsOfBorrowingsClassifiedAsFinancingActivities, ifrs-full:DividendsPaidClassifiedAsFinancingActivities All elements appearing in the face of the financial statements should be included in a calculation relationship somewhere in the filing.
